    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine sanctę et individuę Trinitatis. Anno ab incarnacione domini
                        nostri Iesu Christi millesimo centesimo nono, quintodecimo kalendas aprelis,
                        indicione secunda. <rs key="#Transactional_breve">Breve recordationi</rs>
                        pro futuris temporibus ad memoriam retinendum qualiter <rs key="#Countess"
                            >comitissa</rs>
                        <persName
                            key="#Countess #childOf #Transactional_breve #milesOf #Albergaria/gifori #Intercessory"
                            ref="#people/125">Matilda</persName>, <rs key="#childOf">filia</rs>
                        quondam <persName key="#Marquis/duke #parentOf" ref="#people/1"
                            >Bonefacii</persName> qui fuit <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux et
                            marchio</rs>, fecit cartulam concessionis a presenti die <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Transactional_breve #Albergaria/gifori"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti quod est scitum iuxta
                            fluvium Padi</orgName>, nominative de <placeName
                            key="#Islands Castle #Burgi #Albergaria/gifori" ref="#places/2400"><rs
                                key="#Islands">insula</rs> ubi iam dictum monasterium est
                            edificatum</placeName>, in qua insula extat <rs key="Castle"
                            >castrum</rs> et <placeName key="#Burgi" ref="#places/2418"><rs
                                key="#Burgi">burgum</rs> Gubernoli</placeName>. Sed <rs key="#Intercessory">peticione</rs>
                        eiusdem dominę, <persName key="#Abbots #Monasteries" ref="#people/2189"
                            >Albericus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> supradicti monasterii concessit ei iam dictum
                        castrum et burgum, eo tinore ordine ut quamdiu ipsum castrum vel burgum ibi
                        permanserit, iam dicta domina vel qui in eius loco successerit persolvat
                        suprascripto abbati <rs key="#Census">solidos centum Lucensis monetę</rs>
                        vel eius successoribus in festivitate videlicet Sancti Martini aut infra
                        eius octavam. Si vero iam dictum castrum et burgum, vel per eandem dominam
                        vel per eius successores, exinde tultum vel translatum fuerit, area eiusdem
                        castri et burgi in prefati monasterii potestate persistat. Hoc etiam iam
                        dictus abbas peticioni eiusdem dominę
                        concessit, ut beneficia quę <rs key="#milesOf">milites</rs> ipsius domine in
                        <geogName key="#Curtes #Agricultural_workers #Albergaria/gifori" ref="#estates/80"><rs
                                key="#Curtes">curte</rs> Villule</geogName> vel in eadem insula
                        Sancti Benedicti eatenus ab ipsa tenuerant, deinceps sicut et proprius ex
                        parte ipsius teneant; ipsa vero domina pro eis iam dieta beneficia eidem
                        monasterio serviat. <rs key="#Albergaria/gifori">Albergariam</rs> quoque <rs
                            key="#Agricultural_workers">villanorum</rs> de curte Villulę, vel de
                        insula Sancti Benedicti, quam ipsa domina usque tunc habuerat iam dictus
                        abbas eadem concessit: hii sunt autem <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"
                                ><name ref="Zaccarellus">Zacharellus</name></persName> cum manso
                        uno; <persName key="#Agricultural_workers #Consortes/shared_possessions"
                                ><name ref="Martinus/montanarius">Martinus</name>
                            montanarius</persName> eiusque <rs key="#Consortes/shared_possessions"
                            >consortes</rs> cum manso uno; <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers #Consortes/shared_possessions"><name
                                ref="Iohannes/Bonizo">Iohannes Bonizo</name></persName> et eius
                        consortes cum manso uno; <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name
                                ref="Dominicus">Dominicellus</name></persName> cum manso uno;
                            <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Dominicus/de Aggere"
                                >Dominicus</name> de Aggere</persName> cum quarta parte mansi unius.
                        Post decessum vero iam dicte dominę tam hec albergaria villanorum istorum,
                        quam beneficia militum iam nominata, deveniant in potestate iam nominati
                        monasterii sicut in cartula concessionis continetur. Si quis vero contra hoc
                        facere temptaverit sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">libras
                            centum</rs> et post penam solutam presens hec conventio in sua firmitate
                        permaneat. Actum <placeName ref="#places/2414">Gunzacha</placeName>
                        feliciter. Matilda Dei gratia si quid est subscripsi. Ibi erat <persName
                            key="#Witness #Transactional_breve" ref="#people/3500">Ardoinus de
                            Palude</persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Transactional_breve"
                            ref="#people/2193">Saso de Bibianello</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Transactional_breve" ref="#people/3782">Rodulfus
                            Piloso</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Transactional_breve #childOf" ref="#people/3780"
                            >Gerardus</persName> filius <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Boso"
                                >Bosonis</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Transactional_breve"><name ref="Rodelandus/camerarius"
                                >Rolandus</name> camerarius</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Transactional_breve" ref="#people/3517">Opizo de Gonzaga
                        </persName> qui fuerunt <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs> rogati. </ab>
                </div>
